getPartitionKeyValues

public static boolean getPartitionKeyValues(oracle.jbo.ApplicationModule am,
                                            oracle.jbo.ViewObject vo,
                                            java.util.Map seedArgsMap)
Get the Taxonomy Partition Key values based on the partitioning method, ModuleId or AppId, and display the values to user for selection. Add the return selected values as seedArgsMap entry.

Parameters:
am - ApplicationModule
vo - ViewObject
seedArgsMap - seed arguments map to add selected values
Returns:
true ok, false if user cancelled dialog
